query:
UPDATE subscription_limits
            SET tier = $2,
                max_scans_monthly = $3,
                max_api_calls_monthly = $4,
                max_members = $5,
                max_repos = $6,
                max_private_repos = $7,
                scan_results_retention_days = $8,
                features = $9,
                updated_at = $10
            WHERE organization_id = $1
